    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A majestic mountain and its loyal yeti have had enough of reckless climbers littering their sacred slopes with garbage, frozen corpses, and endless prancing on the peak. It’s time to take a stand against this existential threat—your mission is simple: <strong>Kill The Climbers!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257560/extras/98b86dda9cd6637839dc59369cf21867.poster.avif?t=1746591142\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257560/extras/98b86dda9cd6637839dc59369cf21867.webm?t=1746591142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257560/extras/98b86dda9cd6637839dc59369cf21867.mp4?t=1746591142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Choose Your Defender:</strong> Play as the mighty mountain or its fierce yeti, each with a unique playstyle to master!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unleash Nature’s Fury:</strong> As the mountain, summon rockslides and gusts of wind to sweep climbers away—or fling deadly snowballs as the yeti!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Avalanche Power:</strong> Overwhelmed? Trigger the devastating Avalanche ability to wipe the screen clean!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quick, Intense Runs:</strong> Dive into super-fast 15-minute sessions—perfect for a coffee break!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Climber Chaos:</strong> Face thousands of climbers, including unique types with diverse strengths and weaknesses to exploit!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive the Waves:</strong> Endure 60-second waves, taking down as many climbers as you can!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grow Stronger:</strong> Upgrade your abilities, defenses, and power through in-game progression and meta unlocks!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the fight to protect the peak in this retro arcade showdown—will your mountain prevail?  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257560/extras/7ca17dce21ce33e16617e450ba689d7a.poster.avif?t=1746591142\" width=800 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257560/extras/7ca17dce21ce33e16617e450ba689d7a.webm?t=1746591142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2257560/extras/7ca17dce21ce33e16617e450ba689d7a.mp4?t=1746591142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
